<p style="text-align:start"><strong>Harbor House Rehabilitation &amp; Nursing Center &bull;</strong> located in Hingham, Massachusetts, is a 138-bed skilled nursing center offering&nbsp;<a href="http://www.welchhrg.com/ma-nursing-home-rehabilitation-facility/hingham/short-term-rehab" style="outline: none; color: rgb(17, 113, 169); text-decoration: none;" target="_blank">short-term rehabilitation</a>, and&nbsp;long-term care. Distinctive services at Harbor House include the&nbsp;<a href="http://www.welchhrg.com/ma-nursing-home-rehabilitation-facility/hingham/short-stay-unit" style="outline: none; color: rgb(17, 113, 169); text-decoration: none;">Short Stay Unit</a>&nbsp;for post-hospital transitional care providing a specialized orthopedic program, cardiac &amp; pulmonary care, post-operative recovery, wound care and diabetes disease management.</p>  <p style="text-align:start">Established in 1995, Harbor House employs a staff dedicated to the provision of high quality medical, nursing and rehabilitative care. Compassion and support are the hallmarks of care at Welch Family rehabilitation and nursing centers. The center&rsquo;s goal is to allow every resident to experience the best quality of care and life while maintaining or regaining function, health and well-being.</p>  <p style="text-align:start">Harbor House is located in Hingham, off Route 3A near the harbor and downtown shopping. Situated on a quiet residential street, the nursing center opens onto a beautiful, sunny courtyard with a shaded patio. In addition, residents and families can enjoy our pub, library and Island Lounge, which includes a Plasma TV. Harbor House amenities and services are designed to enhance a resident&rsquo;s stay.</p>  <p style="text-align:start">Harbor House is accredited by&nbsp;<a href="http://www.jointcommission.org/" style="outline: none; color: rgb(17, 113, 169); text-decoration: none;" target="_blank">The Joint Commission</a>. The center is also Medicaid/Medicare Certified and accepts coverage from many private insurers.</p>  <ul style="list-style-type:disc; margin-left:40px"> 	<li><span style="color:#6699cc">Click here for our Rehabilitation Brochure</span></li> </ul> 